text: thumb Schoondijke is a village in the Dutch province of Zeeland. It is located in the municipality of Sluis, about 5 km south of Breskens. Schoondijke was a separate municipality until 1970, when it was merged with Oostburg. ==References== ==External links== * Map of the former municipality, around 1868.
